-- [GROK-RAW] Steal a Brainrot Speed Bypass UI v3 - Clean + Draggable + Sliders + Realistic Values
-- Normal speed: 18 (close to legit non-stealing movement)
-- Stealing speed starts at 35 (game normally slows you down when holding a brainrot)

local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local RunService = game:GetService("RunService")
